---

---

<div
  class="flex flex-col w-full items-center justify-center gap-8 h-auto md:w-vw-custom">
  <div
    class="border rotate-3 flex-col lg:flex-row mt-16 rounded-lg gap-4 p-5 justify-center items-center md:p-10 flex w-4/5 text-gray-900 shadow-2xl dark:shadow-slate-700 hover:shadow-lg dark:hover:shadow-slate-800 duration-200">
    <div class="ld:w-1/3 w-full m-auto">
      <h4
        class="dark:text-white text-black text-2xl md:text-3xl font-extrabold flex items-center">
        Sobre mi
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          class="icon icon-tabler icon-tabler-user w-8 h-8 ml-2 dark:stroke-white"
          width="44"
          height="44"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke-width="1.5"
          stroke="#2c3e50"
          fill="none"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path>
          <path d="M8 7a4 4 0 1 0 8 0a4 4 0 0 0 -8 0"></path>
          <path d="M6 21v-2a4 4 0 0 1 4 -4h4a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v2"></path>
        </svg>
      </h4>
      <p class="text-base ld:text-lg dark:text-white text-black">
        Me llamo Carlos Dominguez. soy un apacionado desarrollador de software
        que cada dia busca especializarce en crear soluciones tecnologicas e
        innovadoras que transformen conceptos en productos funcionales.
      </p>
    </div>

    <img
      width="200"
      height="200"
      src="../../images/person.png"
      alt="img-prilfe"
      class="order-1 object-cover w-64 h-full p-1 md:order-2 rotate-3 lg:p-2 lg:w-64 aspect-square rounded-2xl bg-black/20 dark:bg-yellow-500/5 ring-1 ring-black/70 dark:ring-white/20"
      style="object-position: 50% 50%"
    />
  </div>
</div>
